## Test Excel Workbook

Let's see what an Excel workbook looks like:

```{r excel, echo=FALSE}
template <- read.xlsx("xlsx/template.xlsx", sheet=1)
template <- template %>% select(!contains("XML"))
myft <- flextable(template)
myft <-theme_box(myft)
myft <- autofit(myft)
myft
```
